      <title>當地媒體報道泰國外交部長辭職</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-foreign-minister-resigns-local-media-report-2024-04-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據當地媒體週日報道，泰國外交部長帕普雷·巴希達-努卡拉在內閣改組中失去副總理職務後突然辭職。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-foreign-minister-resigns-local-media-report-2024-04-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
